    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1906-04-17T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1906-04-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="551"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d551">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Russell</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Caracas</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-04-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 17, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Russell asks to be informed if he is to join his colleagues in note to the
                    Government, embodying the department’s views as stated in No. 35, of 2d of
                    April.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
